snippet.title: Super Mario Galaxy Multiplayer - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the creator of this hack, Mr. Brocoli!
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxutxnJ7rjHnUIUcDWcTElQ
Check out his discord server!
https://discord.gg/XuDXxbsATV

DOWNLOAD INFORMATION:
You can join the creator's discord server to find out more about the mod and how to download it! (there's even a splitscreen version being made)

Super Mario Galaxy Multiplayer has made it's way to console and since I've also finally got a second nunchuk, I can now play Super Mario Galaxy with my brother! Make sure you go support my brother by subscribing to his channel!

LukeSkiller: https://youtube.com/channel/UCyQYy_-qpXXSksLrfAoksVg

My Discord Server: https://discord.gg/ErCZRUW
My Twitter Account: https://twitter.com/SPG642
My Twitch Profile: https://www.twitch.tv/spg64

Thanks for watching this trailer! :)
